  <scopecontent id="aspace_ee69fe5273fb08a492a07719f904a702">
    <head>Scope and Contents</head>
<p>The Ruth Maslin Governor's Scholars research files (dated 1980-1988; 0.45 cubic feet; 1 box) comprise research files on the Kentucky Governor's Scholars program compiled by Ruth Maslin, including correspondence, newsletters, newspaper clippings, programs, handbooks, and other materials. The bulk of the collection contains articles and news clippings pertaining to the institution and operation of the Governor's Scholars Program as well as information from the US Department of Education. Also included are letters and articles by the scholars and photographs of the first day of the program.</p>  </scopecontent>
